			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1321475">
									

<p>To someone completely ignorant of taxonomy (such as myself), &quot;The effect of SCP-889 has not been demonstrated to apply to prokaryotes or eukaryotes other than animals or plants.&quot; doesn't make much sense.<br />
